Interface NNCalcModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NNCalcModel1

    public interface NNCalcModel
    Model interface. The Natural Number Calculator model consists of the top and bottom operands (which have only getter methods).
    Mathematical Model (abstract value and abstract invariant of this):
     type NNCalcModel is modeled by
   (top: NATURAL_NUMBER,
    bottom: NATURAL_NUMBER)
    Constructor(s) (initial abstract value(s) of this):
     default:
  ensures
   this = (0, 0)
